N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 641.2 - Utilities exempted

State Regulations
(a) The
provisions of this Part shall not apply to telephone corporations having 25
stations or less. (b) Each
telephone corporation having 25 stations or less is exempted from filing an
annual report unless otherwise ordered by this commission. Notes
